<link href="adcp.css" rel="stylesheet"><entry><xh5>leave it to someone • leave someone to it</xh5><p> <i>leave it to someone—</i>let another person deal with a matter: The professionals all take a greater share of responsibility if a project is to be a success instead of <u>leaving it to</u> the “jack of all trades”—the project engineer.</p><p> <i>leave someone to it—</i>leave a person alone to proceed with smth. without interfering with his work: He is professional enough to know what needs doing so I just <u>left him to it</u>.</p> </entry>
